.lead
  Invalid configuration value
- case size
- when :short
  %div
    = "The config variable #{suggestion.name} has an unexpected value of #{suggestion.value}."

- when :full
  %p
    = "The config variable #{suggestion.name} has an unexpected value of #{suggestion.value}."
  %p
    An invalid admin console configuration may affect suggestions for capacity planning.  Check your configuration in 
    %pre
      = File.join(OpenShift::Config::PLUGINS_DIR, "openshift-origin-admin-console.conf")